/** Scriptnode Visualisation 101


If you need a full 2D plot of the signal, use Option 1.

If you only need a one-dimensional value that shows the current value
(for stuff like mod-rings around a knob or VU meters), I would suggest Option 2.

The scriptnode network here is just a mod chain with a slow LFO that is fed
into a peak node and a global_cable node.
